-- Israel's El Al buys 4 Boeing 777s for $540 million
-- 
-- Sun Mar 16, 2008 7:07am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/03/16/us-elal-boeing-order-idUSL1639070720080316

 

 TEL AVIV  (Reuters) - El Al Israel Airlines ( ELAL.TA ) said on Sunday it had ordered four Boeing Co ( BA.N ) 777-200ER planes for $540 million. 

 The aircraft will be equipped with Rolls Royce engines and be used on medium- and long-haul routes. Three will be delivered in 2012 and one in January 2013. (Reporting by Tova Cohen; Editing by  Jason Neely )